==============================================================================
                    Release of version 0.03 of Perl6::Say
==============================================================================


Perl6/Say version 0.01
======================

DESCRIPTION

Implements the Perl 6 'say' built-in
(i.e. 'print' with an automagically appended "\n")

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

None.

COPYRIGHT AND LICENCE

